VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \bclass\s+\w+\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:memset\s*\(|sanitize|redact|encrypt|mask && MISSING:test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects passing class objects that may leak sensitive information across trust boundaries.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Information Leakage Across Trust Boundaries: Security Risk.
